TextEng: Who are you?
I'm here to kill you. That's the only way.
I have some silver charms. Will you use one?
Text: 은 부적들을 가지고 있어. 하나 쓸래?

TextEng: Me musts know who you be, yuh?
Text: 나 너 누군지 알아야 해, 알지?

TextEng: Me gots to kill you. No offense, huh?
Text: 나 너 죽여야 해. 기분 나쁘게 생각 말고, 응?

TextEng: Me gots silver charms. Fix you up, all good!
Text: 나 은 부적들 가지고 있어. 너 고쳐줄게, 다 좋아질 거야!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> These are cures. They'll restore you.
I'm here to kill you or cure you. You pick which I do.
Text: 널 죽이거나 치료하러 왔어. 네가 골라.

TextEng: Prepare yourself for death then.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You want get fixed, yuh? Take this.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 너 고쳐지고 싶지, 응? 이거 받아.

TextEng: Me kill or cure you. You picks, yuh?
Text: 나 너 죽이거나 치료해. 너 고르는 거야, 알지?

TextEng: Me kill you, stop this plague, yuh.
Text: 나 너 죽여서 이 역병 멈춰, 알지.

TextEng: Who you gives ring to?
You gave your ring away? To whom?
How did you ever become a werewolf?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> I've been sent to end the werewolf menace. If you give me your ring, I will leave and no one will come searching for you in the future.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 늑대인간 위협을 끝내러 파견됐어. 반지를 주면, 떠날게. 그러면 앞으로 아무도 널 찾지 않을 거야.

TextEng: I'll go find help for you. Just stay here.
Me gets help, yuh? You stays here!
Text: 나 도움 받아올게, 알지? 너 여기 있어!

TextEng: Uh, wha' happen to you?
Just give me your ring.
What happened to Bran?
Did Ander survive? Where is he now?
Is Geth all right? Do you know where I could find him?
Text: 게스는 괜찮아? 어디서 찾을 수 있는지 알아?

TextEng: Where is Sir Karathis now?
What happens to Bran, yuh?
Where Ander went? He okay?
Is Geth still alive? Can you help me find him?
Text: 게스 아직 살아 있어? 찾는 거 도와줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Where Sir Karathis be?
Let us speak of something else.
We talk 'bout something else.
